        "func": "var lookup = global.get(\"devicenames\")\nvar now = new Date(Date.now());\nif(msg.succes){\n    lookup[msg.req.params.imei].succes++; \n    global.set(\"devicenames\", lookup);\n    node.status({ fill: \"green\", shape: \"ring\", text: \"name: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].name + \"\\n failed: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].failed + \"\\tsucces: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].succes + \"\\n\" + \"timedstamp: \" + now.toString() });\n    return msg;\n} else{\n    lookup[msg.req.params.imei].failed++; \n    node.status({ fill: \"red\", shape: \"ring\", text: \"name: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].name + \"\\nfailed: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].failed + \"\\tsucces: \" + lookup[msg.req.params.imei].succes + \"\\n\" + \"timedstamp: \" + now.toString() });\n    global.set(\"devicenames\", lookup);\n    throw new Error(\"size was to small skipping this picture\");\n}\n\n",
